location.query:
SELECT 
    u.[Id],
    
	  CASE 
		WHEN u.[CreatedById] IS NULL THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		ELSE u.[CreatedById]
	  END AS [CreatedById],
    
	  CASE 
		WHEN u.IsDisabled = 0 THEN 'Active'
		ELSE 'Disabled'
	  END AS [Status],
    u.[UpdatedById],
    u.[UpdatedOn],
    u.[Username],
    u.[DisplayName],
    u.[FirstName],
    u.[MiddleName],
    u.[LastName],
    u.[Email],
    u.[Position],
    u.[IsDisabled],
    u.[EmailVerified],
    u.[Note],
    u.[IsSystem],
    u.[LastLogin],
    u.[ApprovedById],
    u.[ApprovedOn],
    u.[KeycloakUserId],
    urd.CreatedOn,
    urd.UserId,
    ua.AgencyId, 
    STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') AS Roles,
    CASE 
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%System Administrator%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES Financial Reporter%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%SRES Financial%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
             
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Agency Administrator%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Real Estate Analyst%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Real Estate Manager%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001'
             
        WHEN STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Assistant Deputy Minister Assistant%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Assistant Deputy Minister%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%Executive Director%'
             OR STRING_AGG(urd.RoleName, ', ') LIKE '%View Only Properties%' THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002'
	   
    END AS UserType
FROM Users u
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT 
        ur.UserId,
        MAX(ur.CreatedOn) AS CreatedOn,
        STRING_AGG(r.Name, ', ') AS RoleName
    FROM [pims].[dbo].[UserRoles] ur
    INNER JOIN Roles r ON ur.RoleId = r.Id
    GROUP BY ur.UserId
) AS urd ON u.Id = urd.UserId

LEFT OUTER JOIN (
    SELECT UserId, MIN(AgencyId) AS AgencyId
    FROM UserAgencies
    GROUP BY UserId
) ua_min ON u.Id = ua_min.UserId
LEFT OUTER JOIN UserAgencies ua ON u.Id = ua.UserId AND ua.AgencyId = ua_min.AgencyId

WHERE u.Id <> '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'

GROUP BY u.[Id],
    u.[CreatedById],
    u.[UpdatedById],
    u.[UpdatedOn],
    u.[Username],
    u.[DisplayName],
    u.[FirstName],
    u.[MiddleName],
    u.[LastName],
    u.[Email],
    u.[Position],
    u.[IsDisabled],
    u.[EmailVerified],
    u.[Note],
    u.[IsSystem],
    u.[LastLogin],
    u.[ApprovedById],
    u.[ApprovedOn],
    u.[KeycloakUserId],
    urd.CreatedOn, 
    urd.UserId, 
    ua.AgencyId
ORDER BY urd.CreatedOn ASC

SELECT p.[Id],
	  CASE 
		WHEN p.[CreatedById] IS NULL THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		ELSE p.[CreatedById]
	  END AS [CreatedById],
    p.[CreatedOn],
    p.[UpdatedById],
    p.[UpdatedOn],
    p.[Name],
    p.[Description],
    p.[ClassificationId],
    p.[AgencyId],
    p.[IsSensitive],
    p.[IsVisibleToOtherAgencies],
    p.[PID],
    p.[PIN],
    p.[LandArea],
    p.[LandLegalDescription],
    p.[Zoning],
    p.[ZoningPotential],
    p.[NotOwned],
	CONVERT(VARCHAR(40), CAST(Location.Long AS DECIMAL(18, 14))) + ', ' + CONVERT(VARCHAR(40), CAST(Location.Lat AS DECIMAL(18, 14))) AS Location,
    CASE 
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'The Corporation of the City of Nelson' THEN 188
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Township of Langley' THEN 150
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'District of North Vancouver' THEN 196
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Coombs' THEN 483
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Brookmere' THEN 481
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Thornhill' THEN 501
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Two Mile' THEN 502
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Crofton' THEN 484
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'East Sooke' THEN 485
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Mudge Island' THEN 492
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Coal Harbour' THEN 482
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Miworth' THEN 490
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Lake Errock' THEN 489
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Black Creek' THEN 479
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Whaletown' THEN 504
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Quathiaski Cove' THEN 494
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Big Bay in Stuart Island' THEN 478
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Surge Narrows in Read Island' THEN 500
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Rock Bay in Sayward' THEN 497
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Granite Bay in Quadra Island' THEN 487
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Moberly Lake' THEN 491
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Quatsino' THEN 495
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Bouchie Lake' THEN 480
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'West Lake' THEN 503
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Salmon Valley' THEN 498		
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Red Rock' THEN 496
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Stoner' THEN 499
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Pineview FFG' THEN 493
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Wonowon' THEN 506
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Halfway River' THEN 488
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Giscome' THEN 486
        WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Willow River' THEN 505
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Lower Nicola' THEN 314
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Belcarra' THEN 425
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Tsawwassen' THEN 315
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Anmore' THEN 432
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Lake Cowichan' THEN 442
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'North Cowichan' THEN 450
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Port Edward' THEN 347
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Spallumcheen' THEN 318
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Jumbo Glacier Mountain Resort Municipality' THEN 438
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Kent' THEN 439
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Highlands' THEN 348
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Slocan' THEN 380
		WHEN a.AdministrativeArea = 'Warfield' THEN 448
        ELSE aa.Id 
    END AS AdministrativeAreaId,  
	a.AdministrativeArea,
	a.Address1, 
	a.Postal,
	pp.ParcelId as ParentID,
	0 as PropertyTypeID
FROM 
    [pims].[dbo].[Parcels] p
	INNER JOIN Addresses a
	ON p.AddressId = a.Id
	LEFT OUTER JOIN AdministrativeAreas aa
	ON aa.Name = a.AdministrativeArea
    LEFT OUTER JOIN ParcelParcels pp
    ON pp.SubdivisionId = p.Id

	INNER JOIN Addresses a

SELECT pb.*
  FROM [pims].[dbo].ParcelBuildings pb
  INNER JOIN Buildings b
  ON b.Id = pb.BuildingId
  WHERE b.BuildingPredominateUseId <= 54

SELECT [ParcelId]
      ,[Date]
      ,[Key]
      ,
	  CASE 
		WHEN [CreatedById] IS NULL THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		ELSE [CreatedById]
	  END AS [CreatedById]
      ,[CreatedOn]
      ,[UpdatedById]
      ,[UpdatedOn]
      ,[Firm]
      ,[Value]
      ,[Note]
  FROM [pims].[dbo].[ParcelEvaluations]

      ,[Key]

		WHEN [CreatedById] IS NULL THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		ELSE [CreatedById]
	  END AS [CreatedById]
      ,[CreatedOn]
      ,[UpdatedById]
      ,[UpdatedOn]
      ,[Value]
      ,[Note]
      ,[EffectiveDate]
  FROM [dbo].[ParcelFiscals]

SELECT BuildingId,
  FiscalYear,
  [Key],
  CASE 
		WHEN [CreatedById] IS NULL THEN '00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000'
		ELSE [CreatedById]
	  END AS [CreatedById],
  CreatedOn,
  UpdatedById,
  UpdatedOn,
  [Value],
  Note,
  EffectiveDate
  FROM BuildingFiscals 
  
WHERE BuildingId IN (
	SELECT b.Id 
	FROM Buildings b
	WHERE b.BuildingPredominateUseId <= 54
